    <briefdescription>
<para>This object stores description data that can be used to generate an <ref refid="classDali_1_1Animation" kindref="compound">Animation</ref>. This data can be produced from passing JSON. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This then allows the same description data to be used to repeatedly create an animation multiple times. </para>
